features: Silverware Caddy 4 in 1: The silverware caddy for party has a long opening that can organize 8" paper plates and napkins. The other side is divided into 3 slots which can be used for spoons, forks, and knives. you can use it to carry out to the patio or BBQ at one time

Versatile Silverware Holder: More than just flatware storage! It's up to you to organize what you want with this wooden plastic silverware holder, Great for organizing offices, crafts, and bathrooms, and tidying up space for remotes, pens, crayons, scissors,etc

Minimalist Design & Handcrafted: The utensil holder is handcrafted from solid wood. Great for organizing without taking up too much space, and has a felt bottom so it wouldn't scratch your counter. The condiment caddy is also great for parties and picnics at the park

Compact & Convenient Size: Utensil caddy with a neat and compact size can hold all your utensils, and measures 9”x6”x4.5”. Perfect for keeping silverware neat & easy to access. Free up your drawers and put this caddy in the corner of the counter

Right Gift Choice: The plastic silverware holder is understated and classy. Good for indoor/outdoor parties, picnics, and BBQs, the silverware organizer is suitable for any table setting. Also, it makes a great housewarming gift for family and friends
body.description: DRASTAR Silverware Holder for Party Handcrafted from solid wood DRASTAR functional silverware organizer is a perfect way to declutter your kitchen counter, and table while keeping your utensils within easy reach. A utensil caddy is an excellent addition to festive gatherings, breakrooms, and hospitality suites. Utensil caddy has 3 small compartments on one side and one big compartment on the other side. It kept the plastic silverware and napkins within reach and in place With the napkin holder as part of this, you can get rid of a stand-alone one It is deep & heavy enough that the spoons, knives, and folks won't fall out of it or tip over Plastic utensil holder is sturdy and nice-looking so it goes with any table setting.
